{"tid":1598440,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國核動力列根號帶著最新電子反制，中共國慶前夕靜靜地駛近香港","createTime":"2019-09-27T12:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T13:06:42.000Z","uid":266279,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f696229bd0efe3b58afd87aac168dda0f0a5f977","tid":1598440,"uid":266279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"香港人的怒火，已到大爆發邊緣。核動力列根號帶著最新電子反制，中共國慶前夕靜靜地駛近香港。上次回橫須賀，短時間停留便離開，再直駛菲律賓水域，可謂不尋常。美國情報部門，肯定掌握香港人處境，已到非常危險境地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqTdHTt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqTdHTt.jpg&h=5f3d348a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n列根號 <br />\n艦級 :       尼米茲級<br />\n母港 :       日本橫須賀海軍設施 <br />\n排水量   :  101,400長噸<br />\n動力   :      2座西屋A4W核反應堆<br />\n最高速度 : 30節以上<br />\n乘員 軍艦 :3,200人<br />\n飛行大隊:  2,480人<br />\n武器裝備 : 改進型海麻雀導彈    RIM-116滾體導彈    方陣近迫防禦武器系統<br />\n電戰系統  : SLQ-32A(V)4電戰反制系統    SLQ-25A Nixie魚雷反制系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.usni.org/2019/09/23/usni-news-fleet-and-marine-tracker-sept-23-2019?fbclid=IwAR0wTaxmF5ENpUUv8TkSUZ39IxUBf5F8eYzl7H4QkZ2xabhBtIWQ3W3O93k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.usni.org%2F2019%2F09%2F23%2Fusni-news-fleet-and-marine-tracker-sept-23-2019%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0wTaxmF5ENpUUv8TkSUZ39IxUBf5F8eYzl7H4QkZ2xabhBtIWQ3W3O93k&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=99ecd9bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.usni.org/2019/09/23/usni-news-fleet-and-marine-tracker-sept-23-2019?fbclid=IwAR0wTaxmF5ENpUUv8TkSUZ39IxUBf5F8eYzl7H4QkZ2xabhBtIWQ3W3O93k</a><br />\n<br />\n十一前夕，中美在南海的軍事角力升級。近日有衞星圖片顯示，列根號的美國海軍第7艦隊航空母艦列根號近日在南海航行時，遭7艘解放軍軍艦包圍。中國國防部新聞發言人任國強周四（26日）僅指，美國航母編隊到南海炫耀武力，推動地區軍事化，對此堅決反對。他要求美方切實尊重地區各國的安全關切，為南海的和平穩定貢獻正能量。<br />\n內地網民「浙中指揮長」周二（24日）在微博上載多張解放軍海軍軍艦包圍列根號的衞星圖片，又指列根號周一（23日）被圍期間曾請求派出一架RC135電子偵察機、一架P8A「海神」反潛機赴南海增援。有報道指，列根號當時在獨自航行，其編隊其他艦艇指派往中東執行任務。列根號早前駛離日本基地，一路南下至南海海域。<br />\n任國強在記者會表示，中國駐美國大使崔天凱指本年是中美建交40周年，兩國站在新的十字路口，必須共同承擔歷史責任，對兩國的未來關係作出正確選擇，堅決摒棄新冷戰及文明衝突論，中美合則兩利，鬥則俱傷，合作是唯一正確選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbWbuy7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbWbuy7.jpg&h=07a6b79e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"028b05471df22ae8b422ad5b7b795365028fc94a","tid":1598440,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:41:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fdb99475c6cd16256bfa9cb859688b06992f21d2","tid":1598440,"uid":67325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae16c8ca15d4492b5ab3e16d20341bcbbaaefd9","tid":1598440,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:52:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"11815c447b66e471ae5a0a2c54d6e458a95c2d95","tid":1598440,"uid":128569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"Ww3<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b4e638da4e8eb50f4b6f8a2d37d6ecac97e762","tid":1598440,"uid":48965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11815c447b66e471ae5a0a2c54d6e458a95c2d95","tid":1598440,"uid":128569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"Ww3<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"